{"tid":1565360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日wts收到 關於跳閘 檢控附例4.1b","createTime":"2019-09-13T06:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T08:00:15.000Z","uid":186908,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c5ebd37df18df33851327b5f5d210cc2aee9efea","tid":1565360,"uid":186908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:15:01.000Z","msg":"Whatsapp我有傳過黎 點睇依段野？<br />\n<br />\n一位黨鐵嘅朋友仔通知，各位手足爬山要小心：<br />\n<br />\n可以嘅話，通知兄弟們唔好再跳閘，班popo要我地d職員做完surcharge 另外再檢控附例4.1b<br />\n我們個阿頭點左頭，通知我們前線做附例嘅要做埋4.1b<br />\n班popo 好撚仆街，因為簽左surcharge上到法庭4.1b入梗,然後會等法庭留案底，到讀完大學後所有大公司同埋外國學校外國企業一查你違法行為記錄，會有一條入侵罪嘅案底<br />\n等你永遠搵唔到大機構招聘你，依招好陰毒<br />\n<br />\n有TIU同事話 可以嘅話通知兄弟們唔好再跳閘<br />\n班popo要我地d職員做完surcharge 另外再檢控附例4.1b<br />\n(即以正當使用供進出用的票閘、欄障或旋轉柵閘(如有的話)以外的方式進入或離開該等部分) <br />\n要上法庭審理 最高罰款$5000+有案底"},{"pid":"db078e838682cf104b1d3c8a65f6018f08412935","tid":1565360,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:15:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a1a903b0f4b93d3269daee55abb779c1d9a15de3","tid":1565360,"uid":186908,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:15:40.000Z","msg":"自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWhatsapp有人傳過黎"},{"pid":"02